      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — the same geometry as the COU device. Bovine blood used in vitro; impact of species difference on power-law coefficients assessed via literature meta-analysis (< 6% coefficient variation). All five COU operating points fall within validated flow-speed envelope."
