      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive model selection justified with literature evidence; model form uncertainty estimated.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on rotating machinery benchmark literature; compared against realizable k-ε at two operating points (NIH difference < 4%). Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) used; model form uncertainty ±12% on NIH estimated from alternative model formulations in literature. Uncertainty included in Monte Carlo propagation as epistemic input distribution."
