      "rationale": "In-vitro testing conducted on three independent blood batches per operating point (n=3 per point, 15 total experiments). Between-batch coefficient of variation < 8% for NIH. Sample size supports detection of 15% NIH difference with 80% power at α=0.05. Blood sourced from single species lot to control hematological variability."
